+
+Layer hierarchy:
+    PCNA  (this package)  — phi, psi, omega, guardian, memory tensor fields
+    PCTA  (cores/pcta/)   — circle tensor layer (phase-coordinate transform)
+    PTCA  (cores/ptca/)   — seed tensor routing lattice (53-node graph)
